Why should the Space Army get all the fun toys? Well the Space Nuns certainly think they deserve a super tank. And how do we make a super tank even better? Obviously make it a rolling chapel!

Add them as base decoration, add them as terrain decoration, create tiny war dioramas, do whatever you want with them! Anything is made better with the addition of tiny tanks.

Tiny tanks are intended for resin printers.
